54
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,599
Take good care of Le Yan.

55
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:11,199
Make sure she gets home safely.

56
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:13,680
Chang Ge.

57
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,919
As long as you're holding the Crown Prince's seal,

58
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,319
Hao Du would...

59
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:26,560
