83
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,439
For security purposes,

84
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:01,079
I've had him locked up in my camp.

85
00:06:01,519 --> 00:06:03,240
Wang Jun Kuo is very cunning.

86
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,360
And he has many subordinates.

87
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,800
He might get away.

88
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:07,879
Thank you.

89
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,759
Who are you?

90
00:06:17,759 --> 00:06:18,920
Why are you arresting me?

91
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,199
It's a kid?

92
00:06:20,199 --> 00:06:21,480
Who are you?

93
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,800
Why did you push me?

94
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,879
I've contributed a lot.

95
00:06:24,879 --> 00:06:26,839
I brought help from the camp during the night.

96
00:06:26,839 --> 00:06:28,240
Don't forget to tell this to the court.

97
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,560
I'm waiting for my reward.

98
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,560
I led the rest of the rebels and eliminated...

99
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,639
