- Search the place.

100
00:06:32,639 --> 00:06:33,639
- Yes!
- Yes!

101
00:06:50,759 --> 00:06:51,759
Go!

102
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,600
Where is Chang Ge?

103
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,120
You're asking me?

104
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:25,000
