105
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,160
I have to get her back.

106
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,000
- It's still with her.
- I'm glad you know.

107
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:30,199
If we don't find it,

108
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,120
