109
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,199
Get up now.

110
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:37,720
Go and get her back.

111
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,639
Your partner is still in town.

112
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:46,680
Will he be all right?

113
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:48,040
We made a promise.

114
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,519
I'll leave hints along the path.

115
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,920
He'll come and see me when he gets out.

116
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,920
Thank you for saving my life.

117
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,680
I dare not accept a bow from Your Highness.

118
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:00,319
How do you know?

119
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:04,040
You have a courtly temperament.

120
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:06,079
Other people won't be able to learn it.

121
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:09,839
Rumors have it that Princess Yongning is still missing.

122
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,519
I was once the Crown Prince's subordinate.

123
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:13,120
How could I not recognize you?

124
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:16,560
Wang Jun Kuo even offered to hand you in to the imperial court.

125
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,240
This proves even more that I was right.

126
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:20,000
In that case,

127
00:08:20,519 --> 00:08:22,399
