128
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:25,600
Now, the whole Youzhou is in Li Shi Min's hands.

129
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:28,480
He surely won't let my father's former subordinates go.

130
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,120
Instead of being submissive,

131
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,279
why don't you leave with me?

132
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:32,559
We can work together.

133
00:08:33,450 --> 00:08:34,559
I am a general.

134
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,039
I only follow orders.

135
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,240
General Shen.

136
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:42,000
The whole Youzhou is under Du Ru Hui's control.

137
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:43,919
We can never get Youzhou back.

138
00:08:44,759 --> 00:08:46,240
We'll only be waiting for death here.

139
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:47,559
Besides,

140
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,519
I still have the Crown Prince's seal.

141
00:08:49,519 --> 00:08:51,679
Do you really think a lifeless object...

142
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,360
can mobilize thousands of troops?

143
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:58,840
I'm helping you because I want to repay the Crown Price's kindness.

144
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,330
It's a selfish action.

145
00:09:00,879 --> 00:09:02,090
I'm the Crown Prince's former subordinate,

146
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:04,159
but first, I am a general of Tang.

147
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:07,450
Now, the Ashina Tribe is planning an attack in the north.

148
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,360
Youzhou is an important town in the north.

149
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,840
There are millions of people.

150
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:13,519
My job is to protect...

151
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:14,840
the land of Youzhou.

152
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,960
If I can't even perform my duties,

153
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,210
no matter what you have,

154
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,399
