155
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:24,759
Although I don't agree entirely,

156
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,559
I respect your decisions.

157
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:28,559
I learned something today.

158
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,960
Your Highness, you should leave.

159
00:09:31,279 --> 00:09:33,120
When the chasers arrive,

160
00:09:33,399 --> 00:09:34,840
I will have no choice but to do my job.

161
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,559
I can no longer stay in Youzhou.

162
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:40,120
The world is huge.

163
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,759
Yet, I have nowhere to go.

164
00:09:44,210 --> 00:09:45,279
Go northwest.

165
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:46,639
Go to Shuozhou.

166
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:48,000
It's an isolated place.

167
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,210
It's a piece of land between Tang and the plains.

168
00:09:50,759 --> 00:09:52,639
The royal court won't be able to reach you.

169
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:55,960
Thank you, General Shen.

170
00:09:57,090 --> 00:09:58,919
Take care, Your Highness.

171
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,480
I shall bid you farewell.

172
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,279
Go!

173
00:10:27,039 --> 00:10:28,090
Go!

174
00:10:33,159 --> 00:10:36,159
- Go!
- Go!

175
00:10:49,919 --> 00:10:51,240
Stop.

176
00:10:58,519 --> 00:10:59,759
Your Highness, that's enough.

177
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,480
If we continue, we'll be exhausted.

178
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,879
Didn't you say that jerk has left already?

179
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,240
Why did he come back?

180
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:08,679
I can't let this go.

181
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:10,840
I already observed the surroundings.

182
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,840
There's no trace of an army passing by.

183
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,279
That jerk must have come back alone.

184
00:11:15,519 --> 00:11:16,559
Your Highness.

185
00:11:16,559 --> 00:11:18,200
- What do you want to do?
- He plotted against me.

186
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,600
Why can't I do the same?

187
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:23,120
You should report back to Great Khan in this instance.

188
00:11:23,559 --> 00:11:25,039
If we delay any longer,

189
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,799
Great Khan will get suspicious of us.

190
00:11:27,639 --> 00:11:30,240
Stop telling me what to do and what not to do.

191
00:11:30,679 --> 00:11:32,120
Do you really think that you're my elder brother?

192
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:36,519
So what if Great Khan is suspicious?

193
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:40,080
Am I supposed to just let this go?

194
00:11:41,039 --> 00:11:43,679
Great Khan is leading his men to Shuozhou.

195
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,919
The astringer should be in the north of Shuozhou by now.

196
00:11:46,919 --> 00:11:48,200
Go this way.

197
00:11:49,039 --> 00:11:50,679
If we can guess which route he's taking,

198
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,679
