199
00:11:53,279 --> 00:11:54,320
Yes.

200
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,559
Could they have taken the south route?

201
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,639
Don't you think he would have thought of that already?

202
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:02,080
That jerk is always full of tricks.

203
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,360
He has been after me.

204
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:06,480
