205
00:12:08,279 --> 00:12:10,080
But Great Khan gave him an order.

206
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,480
If he goes this way,

207
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,679
the military line will be delayed.

208
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:19,159
He would do whatever it takes to complete Great Khan's orders.

209
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,840
That's why he'll definitely take the north road.

210
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,519
And I have a feeling that...

211
00:12:24,519 --> 00:12:26,279
he will take the main road on purpose.

212
00:12:26,639 --> 00:12:28,039
We'll cut him off at the main road.

213
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:29,120
We need to be fast.

214
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,159
Pick him up on the side road.

215
00:12:30,639 --> 00:12:31,679
Why?

216
00:12:31,679 --> 00:12:34,200
Because I think he'll take the main road.

217
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,840
I'm sure he expected me to think that.

218
00:12:37,799 --> 00:12:39,120
This time, I bet...

219
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,200
